data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning property features 5 spacious bedrooms and 4 baths providing ample space for your family's needs. The cozy basement features a private 1 bedroom suite with a full bathroom and a comfortable living area. Step outside to the beautiful backyard, perfect for relaxation and outdoor gatherings. Conveniently located near schools, parks, and shopping centers. Don't miss the chance to make this house your forever home!
